{
  "name": "Hardcore Rebalance Pack",
  "author": "AgentKush",
  "fileName": "Hardcore_Rebalance_Pack",
  "version": "1.9",
  "description": "For survivors who think Icarus is too easy. 671 changes across 11 data tables + 2 blueprint overrides. ALPHA HUNTERS (12 named bosses across 255 spawn points with workshop item drops). LIMITED LIVES (Easy=3, Medium=1, Hard=PERMADEATH). ENRAGED CREATURES (3x faster rage, 4.5x longer cooldown). SURVIVAL PRESSURE (reduced HP + slower crafting). REVENGE SPAWNS (longer delays + further distances). CREATURE SCALING on all difficulties. DEADLY LIGHTNING STORMS. BOOSTED KILL XP. WALL-ATTACK FIX. Full coverage across 167 prospects.",
